    # Tasks API

    This section describes the API for managing your tasks.

    ## List tasks

    ```
    GET /tasks.json
    ```

    ### Example

    ```bash
    $ curl  -H 'X-TODO-Token: <username>:<api_key>' \
            http://todo.herokuapp.com/tasks.json
    ```

